\begin_layout Theorem
\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "thm:iso-cross-ratio"

\end_inset

For any partition 
\begin_inset Formula $S_{1},S_{2},S_{3}$
\end_inset

 of a convex body 
\begin_inset Formula $K$
\end_inset

