\end_layout

\begin_layout Exercise
We will need the following relationship between the step-size function and the median step function.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Lemma
\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "lem:step-size"

\end_inset

 We have 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\E_{K}(s(x))\ge\frac{1-\gamma}{\sqrt{n}}.
\]

\end_inset

Moreover,
 for 
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma\ge63/64$
\end_inset

,
 we have 
\begin_inset Formula $F(x)\ge s(x)/32.$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
In the proof of Theorem 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "thm:har-cond"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"
nolink "false"

\end_inset

,
 we will set 
\begin_inset Formula $h(x)=\frac{s(x)}{48\sqrt{n}D}$
\end_inset

.
 We are now ready for that proof.
\end_layout

