\begin_inset Formula $u,v\in K,$
\end_inset

suppose that 
\begin_inset Formula $p,q$
\end_inset

 are the endpoints of the chord through 
\begin_inset Formula $u,v$
\end_inset

 in 
\begin_inset Formula $K$
\end_inset

,
 so that these points occur in the order 
\begin_inset Formula $p,u,v,q.$
\end_inset

