\emph on
cross-ratio
\emph default
 distance between 
\begin_inset Formula $u$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $v$
\end_inset

 is defined as 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
d_{K}(u,v)=\frac{\|u-v\|_{2}\|p-q\|_{2}}{\|p-u\|_{2}\|v-q\|_{2}}.
\]

